OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,FPeople living in a Cumbrian town say
OL,7,Frecent repeated flooding every time it
OL,8,Frains has forced them to leave their
OL,9,Fhomes.
OL,11,FThose effected by the floods in
OL,12,FWhitehaven are blaming a culvert in
OL,13,Fthe Corkickle area for the damage.
OL,14,FThey believe it is overflowing when it
OL,15,Frains, causing water to run through
OL,16,Ftheir gardens and homes.
OL,18,FLinda Bell works as a midwife and says
OL,19,Fshe's had to take a week off of work
OL,20,Fbecause of the stress and the damage
OL,21,Fit has caused.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,FDescribing the recent flooding, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "We couldn't believe our eyes
OL,8,Fbecause there was a literal, I can
OL,9,Fonly describe it as white water
OL,10,Frafting coming down the stairs."
OL,12,FLinda has lived in her home for 20
OL,13,Fyears and she says she has never had
OL,14,Fan issue with flooding - until now.
OL,16,FHer property has been flooded five
OL,17,Ftimes in ten days, forcing her to have
OL,18,Fto live elsewhere.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,FLinda said: "We've had to take up all
OL,7,Fthe flooring, and you need to wear
OL,8,Fwellies to come into your own house,
OL,9,Fbecause you never know what you are
OL,10,Fgoing to deal with."
OL,12,F"It's causing a significant amount of
OL,13,Fstress, I can't concentrate on
OL,14,Fanything. While I can't do anything, I
OL,15,Ffeel like I have to be here, I just
OL,16,Fcan't explain it."
OL,18,FIt's thought a total of five
OL,19,Fproperties have been affected. Linda's
OL,20,Fneighbour, Joe Hanlon, had his decking
OL,21,Fand retaining wall damaged.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,FHe said: "We just want it repaired so
OL,7,Fwe can stop the problem and move on.
OL,9,F"I think it's taken way too long,
OL,10,Fbecause at the end of the day, they
OL,11,Fknow where the problem is, and they've
OL,12,Fknown that since Friday.
OL,14,F"To still put that job off till
OL,15,FTuesday, knowing that every time it
OL,16,Frains, my neighbours and I will be
OL,17,Fflooded without fail."
OL,19,FA culvert is a large pipe that allows
OL,20,Fwater to flow through an obstacle such
OL,21,Fas a road or driveway.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,FThe culvert that has been linked to
OL,7,Fthe flooding is on land that is owned
OL,8,Fby the housing association, Home Group.
OL,10,FTom Cuthill, Home Group's Head of
OL,11,FMaintenance for the North West, said:
OL,12,F"We were notified on June 2nd to the
OL,13,Fflooding issues. We immediately
OL,14,Fcontacted our customers who were
OL,15,Faffected and alternative accommodation
OL,16,Fwas offered and arranged where needed.
OL,17,FOur first priority was to make sure
OL,18,Four customers were safe. Our next, was
OL,19,Fto ascertain what was causing the
OL,20,Fflooding.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,F"This has required a multi-agency
OL,7,Fresponse between Home Group and others
OL,8,Fpartners due to a number of issues
OL,9,Fhaving been highlighted with the
OL,10,Fdrainage with mixed ownership. Some
OL,11,Fworks have already been undertaken by
OL,12,Fpartners to resolve the issue which
OL,13,Fled to an issue being identified on
OL,14,FJune 9th with a culvert on our land."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,F"Following further investigations
OL,7,Fwhich have been undertaken, we have
OL,8,Fidentified the cause of the problem on
OL,9,Four land and we aim to have
OL,10,Fcontractors on site on Tuesday to
OL,11,Fbegin the repair works to the culvert.
OL,12,FWe expect this work to take up to two
OL,13,Fweeks due to a garage needing to be
OL,14,Fdemolished to enable access to the
OL,15,Fsite.
OL,17,F"However, I would stress that the
OL,18,Fdrain is not blocked but its capacity
OL,19,Fis being reduced by an obstruction
OL,20,Fwithin it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,F"I want to apologise for the serious
OL,7,Finconvenience this has caused our
OL,8,Fcustomers, and other residents on Esk
OL,9,FAvenue and assure residents that we,
OL,10,Falong with partners are doing
OL,11,Feverything we can to resolve the issue
OL,12,Fas soon as we possibly can."
OL,14,FA Cumberland Council spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "We understand how distressing
OL,16,Fthis has been for residents and we are
OL,17,Fcontinuing to work closely with
OL,18,Fpartners to resolve the issue as
OL,19,Fquickly as possible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@GOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,F"Following reports of flooding on 2
OL,7,FJune, United Utilities and Cumberland
OL,8,FCouncil highways officers attended the
OL,9,Fsite to investigate.
OL,11,F"Investigations have identified that
OL,12,Fthe flooding is linked to a blockage
OL,13,Fwithin a culverted watercourse on
OL,14,Fprivate land. The land owner has been
OL,15,Finformed and asked to take urgent
OL,16,Faction to address the issue.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781542112
OL,3,CMidwife 'couldn't believe her eyes' as
OL,4,Chome floods for fifth time in ten days
OL,6,F"In the meantime, Cumberland Council
OL,7,Fhighways officers have made the area
OL,8,Fsafe, and our teams continue to work
OL,9,Fwith all parties to reduce the risk of
OL,10,Ffurther flooding."
OL,12,FA United Utilities spokesperson, said:
OL,13,F"We have carried out several
OL,14,Finvestigations and found no issues
OL,15,Fwithin our network that would have
OL,16,Fcaused flooding. We supported the
OL,17,Fcouncil with their investigation this
OL,18,Fweek and believe the issue could be
OL,19,Fcoming from a culvert that is not part
OL,20,Fof our network."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]uD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
